<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713fdbc5ca195391b995e01f77dead92843cd516","tid":2516303,"uid":325716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24c1f35a8509d0a71706af84eee0ec2ee40328a4","tid":2516303,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b59777986cabfe81712ac5dddbf7e571c5cbf8a7","tid":2516303,"uid":325716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"308da974b527c0eb302c04b0f1d8aa4c686f9b06","tid":2516303,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T14:55:44.000Z","msg":"我知個規舉係咁<br />\n就係問點解唔可以直接豁免？<br />\n根本有無拆碌都有機會係架地鐵入面整跌整到人<br />\n<br />\n所以就係ON９囉<br />\n<br />\n睇返其他國家係咁既咩？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KT3YriLZhZE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKT3YriLZhZE&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordKxURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=3496addd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KT3YriLZhZE</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好將自己困係井底啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T15:06:26.000Z","msg":"係好on9架<br />\n咁你想點?<br />\n電動車<br />\n白牌車<br />\n街邊檔<br />\n跟唔上時代嘅嘢多到數唔清<br />\n你又有咩錯覺覺得呢度唔係井底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T15:20:45.000Z","msg":"我講緊你既眼界呀<br />\n真係咁難明咩<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>電動車  <br />\n白牌車  <br />\n街邊檔  <br />\n跟唔上時代嘅嘢多到數唔清</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以你邏輯<br />\n咁呢抽野係咪唔撚屌得先<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係香港係咪要含撚含到要屌鳩啲提出呢啲野有問題既人先至係正常做法<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁邊個開PO屌鳩政府屌鳩林鄭屌鳩黑警你係咪會衝出黎叫佢地收聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T18:06:07.000Z","msg":"叻叻啦<br />\n咁你屌完有咩唔同左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港單車本嚟就係小眾<br />\n要大眾就小眾本身就身就無咩討論空間<br />\n又唔見你用人口密度同外國比<br />\n講到鐵好多位比你泊單身咁<br />\n最撚仆街嘅係收工時間隊架車上去<br />\n仲要係打橫放<br />\n一架單車霸一排櫈位<br />\n搞乜鳩?<br /